(1, 'ServiceSteps', '2016-08-01 13:57:33', '2016-06-01 03:16:05', 'WEB DESIGN', 'I design websites for small to medium business and organisations. Your website is designed to fulfil your expectations, and your customers expectations. It\'s important that your website looks good to engage your visitors, allowing your website to become successful and meet the goals you are striving for.', 'fa-edit', 1, 6),
(2, 'ServiceSteps', '2016-06-01 03:26:14', '2016-06-01 03:16:37', 'WEB DEVELOPMENT', 'I custom develop all websites, allowing them to remain unique, scalable and to function as required. Your website will perform better, be more efficient, and overall it will provide a better experience for you and your users. Whatever your idea, I can turn it in to a reality.', 'fa-code', 2, 6),
(3, 'ServiceSteps', '2016-06-01 03:22:24', '2016-06-01 03:22:19', 'HTML5 & CSS3', 'I create websites that use the latest HTML5 and CSS3 and Bootstrap technology, this allows me to deliver cutting edge functionality in a beautiful responsive website designs. With more businesses online than ever before, distinguishing yourself from the crowd has never been more essential for your business to succeed.', 'fa-html5', 3, 6),
(4, 'ServiceSteps', '2016-06-01 03:24:18', '2016-06-01 03:24:04', 'SEO', 'Everyone understands the importance of getting their website listed on the first page of Google. I carry out Search Engine Optimization practices on every page of every website I create, allowing your site to rank higher in search engine results - potentially driving more traffic to your site.', 'fa-search', 4, 6),
(5, 'ServiceSteps', '2016-06-01 04:07:58', '2016-06-01 03:24:44', 'MOBILE RESPONSIVE', 'Are you missing out on mobile devices? If you don’t have a mobile website, then you are missing out on customers. I use the latest “responsive design” techniques to ensure your business website works well on any mobile devices, as it does on a desktop or laptop.', 'fa-mobile', 5, 6),
(6, 'ServiceSteps', '2016-06-01 03:25:38', '2016-06-01 03:25:35', 'CONTENT MANAGEMENT', 'All websites are built using a Content Management System in either WordPress or SilverStripe. This allowing you to keep your websites content updated and current, with no knowledge of HTML or web development skills. You are able to manage your website yourself, from anywhere at anytime.', 'fa-tasks', 6, 6),
(7, 'ServiceSteps', '2016-06-01 03:27:24', '2016-06-01 03:27:13', 'PHOTOGRAPHY', 'A lot of clients require photos taken of their work or business to put on their website. I can help with this. I will arrange a date and time with you and then arrive and take pictures for you.', 'fa-camera', 7, 6),
(8, 'ServiceSteps', '2016-06-01 03:27:50', '2016-06-01 03:27:44', 'WEBSITE HOSTING', 'I offer hosting and domain name for your website without you worrying about what you need to buy or what add on you may or may not need. All I do need to know is the desired domain name you wish to use for your website. If you already have a domain name and hosting for your website, don’t worry.', 'fa-server', 8, 6),
(9, 'ServiceSteps', '2016-06-01 03:28:24', '2016-06-01 03:28:12', 'WEBSITE RE-DESIGN', 'Is your website a few years old, looking tired and need of a makeover? Did you maybe try putting it together yourself by using free website templates or software but realized it doesn’t look professional? Customers will always look at your website before contacting you, so your company’s first impression is crucial to get right.', 'fa-wrench', 9, 6);

