(66, 6, 9, 1, 1, 1, 'Page', '2016-05-22 13:56:35', '2016-04-14 05:57:06', 'services', 'My Services', 'Services', '<section class="services-items-section"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1>What I Can do for You</h1>\n</div>\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-3">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-desktop fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>The websites I design and develop for you is owned by you 100%. All images, text and photos are yours. There are no ties once finished.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-pencil fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>All websites built with CMS allows you to manage the content yourself if required. All CMS will be easy to use and designed for your needs.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-wrench fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>I offer ongoing services and updates of all sites when needed. I am there when you need me.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-code fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>I design, code and test your website to make sure working for all devices before I release the website to you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="services-section normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Web Design</h2>\n<p class="lead">I build websites for business, organizations and professionals. If you are looking for a website, a CMS system like WordPress or SilverStripe or something for your business, organization or any other ideas, but are not sure how it needs to be realized then I can help.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto" src="" title=""></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Web Development</h2>\n<p class="lead">It all starts with your ideas of what you want to achieve on the web. I then guide you through the process in simple no nonsense terms that enable you to achieve what you want on the web.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto" src="" title=""></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7">\n<h2 class="services-heading">HTML5 &amp; CSS3</h2>\n<p class="lead">I create websites that use the latest HTML5 and CSS3 and Bootstrap technology, this allows us to deliver cutting edge functionality in a beautiful responsive website designs. With more businesses online than ever before, distinguishing yourself from the crowd has never been more essential for your business to succeed.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto" src="" title=""></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Mobile Responsive Design</h2>\n<p class="lead">Are you missing out on mobile devices? If you don’t have a mobile website, then you are missing out on customers. I use the latest “responsive design” techniques to ensure your business website works well on any mobile devices, as it does on a desktop or laptop.</p>\n<p>The amount of time and money people are spending on their mobile devices is growing rapidly, but yet many businesses are not “optimized” for the mobile market. I can help grow your business significantly by turning your website into a responsive one and reaching those mobile devices.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto" src="" title=""></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7">\n<h2 class="services-heading">CMS Design</h2>\n<p class="lead">I offer websites build on CMS. These systems allow live editing of websites content, by users with no knowledge of HTML or web development. The following Content Management Systems (CMS) I will mostly be using are:</p>\n<p><strong>WordPress</strong> as the most preferred Content Management System (CMS) creating stunning, future-proof websites. Whether you need a professional WordPress website, a WordPress theme or plugin, Ive got it covered.</p>\n<p><strong>SilverStripe</strong> the intuitive Content Management System (CMS), with an extensible framework. SilverStripe makes it easier to update your site and still have it look professional. No idea is too complex.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto" src="" title=""></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">\n<h2 class="services-heading">SEO</h2>\n<p class="lead">Everyone understands the importance of getting their website listed “organically” on the first page of Google, Bing and Yahoo when your relevant keywords are searched. We can help your websites reach your SEO goals with the correct techniques.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto" src="" title=""></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Photography</h2>\n<p class="lead">A lot of our clients require photos taken of their work or business to put on their website. I can help with this. I will arrange a date and time with you and then arrive and take pictures for you.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto" src="" title=""></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Website Re-Design</h2>\n<p class="lead">Is your website a few years old, looking tired and need of a makeover? Did you maybe try putting it together yourself by using free website templates or software but realized it doesn’t look professional? Customers will always look at your website before contacting you, so your company’s first impression is crucial to get right.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto" src="" title=""></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h2>LET\'S WORK TOGETHER</h2>\n<p>Interested in working together? Get in touch today so we can discuss your reqirements.</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="contact.html">Contact me <span class="fa fa-arrow-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 3, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0, NULL);
