(84, 2, 29, 1, 1, 1, 'Page', '2016-05-24 02:11:23', '2016-04-14 05:54:02', 'about', 'A Little Bit About Me', 'About ', '<section class="about-section"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1>WEB DESIGNER AND DEVELOPER<br><small>based in Kaiapoi, North Canterbury.</small></h1>\n<div class="col-md-4"><img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="assets/Uploads/Mark_Barker-3.jpg" alt="Mark Barker 3" height="275" width="196"></div>\n<div class="col-md-8">\n<p>I love what I do and have a real passion for creating unique designs that are tailored for my clients, bringing creatively to every project I create. I strive to create work that not only pushes myself to exceed, but also help my clients to do better business and become more successful. I am constantly exploring and evolving ideas, which helps better my clients in ways they can target their customers.</p>\n<p>I love what I do and have a real passion for building unique websites that are tailored for you, bringing creatively to every project I build. I strive to create work that not only pushes myself to exceed, but also help you to do better business and be more successful.</p>\n<p>I builds websites for small - medium business, organizations, and personal websites. I can manage and update your site for you or you can have a CMS site like WordPress that you can update and manage yourself.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container fixed-1-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h2>My success depends on my client’s success…</h2>\n<p>I don’t just build websites for my portfolio – I build websites that fulfill the needs of my clients and to meet and exceed their expectations.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<div>\n<h1>Steps I Take</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Discussion</h4>\n<p>I like to meet and get to know you as people and get an idea of what you like and don’t like.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-comments-o fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Ideas</h4>\n<p>I go away and brainstorm your needs and come up with ideas that you can think about.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-desktop fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Design</h4>\n<p>I then design your site and put it through testing where you can see it fully working. At this stage you can make changes to suit your likes and dislikes.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-send-o fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Development</h4>\n<p>After some back and forth I then put your new website together and then put it live for people to look at and appreciate what you do.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container fixed-2-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h3>If you have a vision or a project in mind, I can help you.</h3>\n<p>I take the time to understand your goals and vision which helps me to identify the right approach to target your customers.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h2>LET\'S WORK TOGETHER</h2>\n<p>Interested in working together? Get in touch today so we can discuss your reqirements.</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="contact.html">Contact me <span class="fa fa-arrow-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 2, 1, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0, NULL),
