(102, 1, 6, 1, 1, 1, 'HomePage', '2016-05-25 02:53:17', '2016-04-14 05:54:02', 'home', 'Home', NULL, '<section id="wid" class="normal-bg wid-section"><div class="container">\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span class="fa-stack fa-5x"> <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i> <i class="fa fa-cog fa-stack-1x"></i> </span>\n<h2>WHAT I DO</h2>\n<p>I design and build websites using WordPress CMS or SilverStripe frameworks. I create websites with mobile responsive in mind to reach your customers across mobile devices.</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="services/">My Services <span class="fa fa-arrow-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span class="fa-stack fa-5x"> <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i> <i class="fa fa-share-alt fa-stack-1x"></i> </span>\n<h2>MY PROCESS</h2>\n<p>Creating a new website should be productive and enjoyable process; therefore I work closely with you so when we can form the perfect websites for your business together.</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="about/">View Details <span class="fa fa-arrow-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span class="fa-stack fa-5x"> <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i> <i class="fa fa-mobile fa-stack-1x"></i> </span>\n<h2>MY RESULTS</h2>\n<p>A well put together website that works across modern devices and optimised for search engines. I offer ongoing services and updates of all sites when needed. I am there when you need me.</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="portfolio/">My Portfolio <span class="fa fa-arrow-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h2>MY WORK</h2>\n<p>I focus on details when it comes to designing and developing for websites and mobile responsive devices. I consider every aspect of a project to achieve not just something just great, but works for its purpose.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container fixed-1-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1>WHAT I STRIVE FOR</h1>\n<p>I pride myself on the service I provide for my clients to achieve the resuilts to reach out to their customers.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1 class="text-center">HOW I WORK</h1>\n</div>\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-3 col-xs-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-comments-o fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<h4>PRESENT YOUR IDEA</h4>\n<p>In most cases I will meet face to face to discuss your ideas and what it is your wanting from your website, how you want it to look like and collect any information regarding your business or organization.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-xs-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-pencil-square-o fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<h4>I\'LL GET IDEAS</h4>\n<p>Once I have a clear understanding of your thoughts and ideas, I will go and put together your vision and I will try and make it real for you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-xs-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-wrench fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<h4>I\'LL BUILD IT</h4>\n<p>I then go and build your vision making sure it works and functions as it should and represent your business or organization as it should.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-xs-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-send-o fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<h4>DELIVER YOUR IDEAS</h4>\n<p>As your site is being built, you will be given a means to view it in action as it develops. This is a working process and I’m most likely wont get it right the first time until you are happy with it.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>', 'Freelance Web Designer and Developer, based in Kaiapoi, North Canterbury using SilverStripe', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0, NULL),
(103, 2, 31, 1, 1, 1, 'Page', '2016-05-25 03:26:26', '2016-04-14 05:54:02', 'about', 'A Little Bit About Me', 'About ', '<section class="about-section"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1>WEB DESIGNER AND DEVELOPER<br><small>based in Kaiapoi, North Canterbury.</small></h1>\n<div class="col-md-4"><img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="assets/Uploads/Mark_Barker-1.jpg" alt="Mark Barker 3"></div>\n<div class="col-md-8">\n<p>I love what I do and have a real passion for creating unique designs that are tailored for my clients, bringing creatively to every project I create. I strive to create work that not only pushes myself to exceed, but also help my clients to do better business and become more successful. I am constantly exploring and evolving ideas, which helps better my clients in ways they can target their customers.</p>\n<p>I love what I do and have a real passion for building unique websites that are tailored for you, bringing creatively to every project I build. I strive to create work that not only pushes myself to exceed, but also help you to do better business and be more successful.</p>\n<p>I builds websites for small - medium business, organizations, and personal websites. I can manage and update your site for you or you can have a CMS site like WordPress that you can update and manage yourself.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container fixed-1-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h2>My success depends on my client’s success…</h2>\n<p>I don’t just build websites for my portfolio – I build websites that fulfill the needs of my clients and to meet and exceed their expectations.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<div>\n<h1>Steps I Take</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Discussion</h4>\n<p>I like to meet and get to know you as people and get an idea of what you like and don’t like.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-comments-o fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Ideas</h4>\n<p>I go away and brainstorm your needs and come up with ideas that you can think about.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-desktop fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Design</h4>\n<p>I then design your site and put it through testing where you can see it fully working. At this stage you can make changes to suit your likes and dislikes.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-send-o fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Development</h4>\n<p>After some back and forth I then put your new website together and then put it live for people to look at and appreciate what you do.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container fixed-2-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h3>If you have a vision or a project in mind, I can help you.</h3>\n<p>I take the time to understand your goals and vision which helps me to identify the right approach to target your customers.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 2, 1, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0, NULL),
(104, 6, 14, 1, 1, 1, 'Page', '2016-05-25 03:27:48', '2016-04-14 05:57:06', 'services', 'My Services', 'Services', '<section class="services-items-section normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1>What I Can do for You</h1>\n</div>\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-3">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-desktop fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>The websites I design and develop for you is owned by you 100%. All images, text and photos are yours. There are no ties once finished.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-pencil fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>All websites built with CMS allows you to manage the content yourself if required. All CMS will be easy to use and designed for your needs.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-wrench fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>I offer ongoing services and updates of all sites when needed. I am there when you need me.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-code fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>I design, code and test your website to make sure working for all devices before I release the website to you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="services-section"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Web Design</h2>\n<p class="lead">I build websites for business, organizations and professionals. If you are looking for a website, a CMS system like WordPress or SilverStripe or something for your business, organization or any other ideas, but are not sure how it needs to be realized then I can help.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="../snapwebdesigns.co.nz-ss/" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto"></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Web Development</h2>\n<p class="lead">It all starts with your ideas of what you want to achieve on the web. I then guide you through the process in simple no nonsense terms that enable you to achieve what you want on the web.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="../snapwebdesigns.co.nz-ss/" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto"></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7">\n<h2 class="services-heading">HTML5 &amp; CSS3</h2>\n<p class="lead">I create websites that use the latest HTML5 and CSS3 and Bootstrap technology, this allows us to deliver cutting edge functionality in a beautiful responsive website designs. With more businesses online than ever before, distinguishing yourself from the crowd has never been more essential for your business to succeed.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="../snapwebdesigns.co.nz-ss/" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto"></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Mobile Responsive Design</h2>\n<p class="lead">Are you missing out on mobile devices? If you don’t have a mobile website, then you are missing out on customers. I use the latest “responsive design” techniques to ensure your business website works well on any mobile devices, as it does on a desktop or laptop.</p>\n<p>The amount of time and money people are spending on their mobile devices is growing rapidly, but yet many businesses are not “optimized” for the mobile market. I can help grow your business significantly by turning your website into a responsive one and reaching those mobile devices.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="../snapwebdesigns.co.nz-ss/" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto"></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7">\n<h2 class="services-heading">CMS Design</h2>\n<p class="lead">I offer websites build on CMS. These systems allow live editing of websites content, by users with no knowledge of HTML or web development. The following Content Management Systems (CMS) I will mostly be using are:</p>\n<p><strong>WordPress</strong> as the most preferred Content Management System (CMS) creating stunning, future-proof websites. Whether you need a professional WordPress website, a WordPress theme or plugin, Ive got it covered.</p>\n<p><strong>SilverStripe</strong> the intuitive Content Management System (CMS), with an extensible framework. SilverStripe makes it easier to update your site and still have it look professional. No idea is too complex.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="../snapwebdesigns.co.nz-ss/" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto"></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">\n<h2 class="services-heading">SEO</h2>\n<p class="lead">Everyone understands the importance of getting their website listed “organically” on the first page of Google, Bing and Yahoo when your relevant keywords are searched. We can help your websites reach your SEO goals with the correct techniques.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="../snapwebdesigns.co.nz-ss/" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto"></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Photography</h2>\n<p class="lead">A lot of our clients require photos taken of their work or business to put on their website. I can help with this. I will arrange a date and time with you and then arrive and take pictures for you.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="../snapwebdesigns.co.nz-ss/" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto"></div>\n</div>\n<hr class="services-divider"><div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5">\n<h2 class="services-heading">Website Re-Design</h2>\n<p class="lead">Is your website a few years old, looking tired and need of a makeover? Did you maybe try putting it together yourself by using free website templates or software but realized it doesn’t look professional? Customers will always look at your website before contacting you, so your company’s first impression is crucial to get right.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7"><img class="services-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="../snapwebdesigns.co.nz-ss/" alt="Generic placeholder image" data-src="holder.js/300x300/auto"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 3, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0, NULL),
