(120, 1, 7, 1, 1, 1, 'HomePage', '2016-05-29 17:37:32', '2016-04-14 05:54:02', 'home', 'Home', NULL, '<section id="wid" class="single-container normal-bg wid-section"><div class="container">\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span class="fa-stack fa-5x"> <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i> <i class="fa fa-cog fa-stack-1x"></i> </span>\n<h3>WHAT I DO</h3>\n<p>I design and develop websites using WordPress or SilverStripe. I create websites with mobile responsive in mind to reach your customers across mobile devices.</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="service">My Services <span class="fa fa-arrow-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span class="fa-stack fa-5x"> <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i> <i class="fa fa-share-alt fa-stack-1x"></i> </span>\n<h3>MY PROCESS</h3>\n<p>Creating new websites should be productive and enjoyable process; therefore I work closely with you so we can form the perfect websites for your business together.</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="about">View Details <span class="fa fa-arrow-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12">\n<div class="services-item"><span class="fa-stack fa-5x"> <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i> <i class="fa fa-mobile fa-stack-1x"></i> </span>\n<h3>MY RESULTS</h3>\n<p>A well put together website that works across modern devices and optimised for search engines. I offer ongoing services and updates of all sites when needed.</p>\n<p><a class="btn btn-lg" href="portfolio">My Portfolio <span class="fa fa-arrow-right fa-fw"></span></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h3>MY WORK</h3>\n<p>I focus on details when it comes to designing and developing for websites and mobile responsive devices. I consider every aspect of a project to achieve not just something just great, but works for its purpose.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container fixed-2-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h3>WHAT I STRIVE FOR</h3>\n<p>I pride myself on the service I provide for my clients to achieve the resuilts to reach out to their customers.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1 class="text-center">HOW I WORK</h1>\n</div>\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-comments-o fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<h4>PRESENT YOUR IDEA</h4>\n<p>I will discuss your ideas and what it is your wanting from your project, how you want it to look like and collect any information regarding your business or organization.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-pencil-square-o fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<h4>I\'LL GET IDEAS</h4>\n<p>Once I have a clear understanding of your thoughts and ideas, I will then go away and put together your vision of your project and I will then try and make it real for you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-wrench fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<h4>I\'LL BUILD IT</h4>\n<p>I will then go and develop your vision making sure your project works and functions as it should and that it represent your business or organization as it should.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-send-o fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<h4>DELIVER YOUR IDEAS</h4>\n<p>As your site is being built, you will be given a means to view it in action as it develops. This is a working process and I’m most likely wont get it right the first time until you are happy with it.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>', 'Freelance Web Designer and Developer, based in Kaiapoi, North Canterbury using SilverStripe', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0, NULL),
(121, 2, 33, 1, 1, 1, 'Page', '2016-05-30 12:28:30', '2016-04-14 05:54:02', 'about', 'A Little Bit About Me', 'About ', '<section class="about-section"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1>WEB DESIGNER AND DEVELOPER<br><small>based in Kaiapoi, North Canterbury.</small></h1>\n<div class="col-md-4"><img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" title="" src="assets/Uploads/Mark_Barker-1.jpg" alt="Mark Barker"></div>\n<div class="col-md-8">\n<p>I love what I do and have a real passion for creating unique designs that are tailored for you, bringing creatively to every project I create. I strive to create work that not only pushes myself to exceed, but also help you to do better business and become more successful. I am constantly exploring and evolving ideas, which helps better you in ways they can target your customers.</p>\n<p>I builds websites for small - medium business, organizations, and personal websites. I can manage and update your site for you or you can have a CMS site like WordPress that you can update and manage yourself.</p>\n<p>Hiring a <strong>Freelance Web Designer and Developer</strong> means you get to work one-on-one and collaboratively with the actual person who is actually working on your website.</p>\n<p>This helps ensure your site is right on the money right from the start, with the total flexibility to make any changes you need any time you like. Just pick up the phone and you’re speaking to me — your personal designer and developer – not an agency secretary.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container fixed-2-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h2>My success depends on my client’s success…</h2>\n<p>I don’t just build websites for my portfolio – I build websites that fulfill the needs of my clients and to meet and exceed their expectations.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<div>\n<h1>STEPS I TAKE</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Discussion</h4>\n<p>I like to meet and get to know you as people and get an idea of what you like and don’t like.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-comments-o fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Ideas</h4>\n<p>I go away and brainstorm your needs and come up with ideas that you can think about.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-desktop fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Design</h4>\n<p>I then design your site and put it through testing where you can see it fully working. At this stage you can make changes to suit your likes and dislikes.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">\n<div class="services-item"><i class="fa fa-send-o fa-3x fa-icons"></i>\n<h4>Development</h4>\n<p>After some back and forth I then put your new website together and then put it live for people to look at and appreciate what you do.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h3>If you have a vision or a website in mind, I can help you.</h3>\n<p>I take the time to understand your goals and vision which helps me to identify the right approach to target your customers.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 2, 1, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0, NULL),
(122, 6, 19, 1, 1, 1, 'Page', '2016-05-30 12:30:50', '2016-04-14 05:57:06', 'services', 'My Services', 'Services', '<section class="services-items-section normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1>WHAT I CAN DO FOR YOU</h1>\n</div>\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-4">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-desktop fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>The websites I design and develop for you is owned by you 100%. All images, text and photos are yours. There are no ties once finished.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-4">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-wrench fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>I offer ongoing services and updates of all sites when needed. I am there when you need me.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-4">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-code fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>I design, code and test your website to make sure working for all devices before I release the website to you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="services-section"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-edit fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>WEB DESIGN</h3>\n<p>I design websites for small business, organizations, and personal websites. Your website is designed to fulfill your expectations, and your customers expectations. It\'s important that your website looks good to engage your visitors, allowing your website to become successful and meet the goals you are striving for.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-code fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>WEB DEVELOPMENT</h3>\n<p>I custom develop all websites, allowing them to remain unique, scalable and to function as required. Your website will perform better, be more efficient, and overall it will provide a better experience for you and your users. Whatever your idea, I can turn it in to a reality.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-html5 fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>HTML5 &amp; CSS3</h3>\n<p>I create websites that use the latest HTML5 and CSS3 and Bootstrap technology, this allows me to deliver cutting edge functionality in a beautiful responsive website designs. With more businesses online than ever before, distinguishing yourself from the crowd has never been more essential for your business to succeed.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br><br><div class="row">\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-search fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>SEO</h3>\n<p>Everyone understands the importance of getting their website listed on the first page of Google. I carry out SEO practices on every page of every website I create, allowing your site to rank higher in search engine results - potentially driving more traffic to your site.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-mobile fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>MOBILE RESPONSIVE</h3>\n<p>Are you missing out on mobile devices? If you don’t have a mobile website, then you are missing out on customers. I use the latest “responsive design” techniques to ensure your business website works well on any mobile devices, as it does on a desktop or laptop.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-tasks fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>CONTENT MANAGEMENT</h3>\n<p>All websites are built using a Content Management System in either WordPress or SilverStripe. This allowing you to keep your websites content updated and current, with no knowledge of HTML or web development skills. You are able to manage your website yourself, from anywhere at anytime.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br><br><div class="row">\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-camera fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>PHOTOGRAPHY</h3>\n<p>A lot of clients require photos taken of their work or business to put on their website. I can help with this. I will arrange a date and time with you and then arrive and take pictures for you.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-server fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>WEBSITE HOSTING</h3>\n<p>I offer hosting and domain name for your website without you worrying about what you need to buy or what add on you may or may not need. All I do need to know is the desired domain name you wish to use for your website. If you already have a domain name and hosting for your website, don’t worry.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-wrench fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>WEBSITE RE-DESIGN</h3>\n<p>Is your website a few years old, looking tired and need of a makeover? Did you maybe try putting it together yourself by using free website templates or software but realized it doesn’t look professional? Customers will always look at your website before contacting you, so your company’s first impression is crucial to get right.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h2>TOOLS AND PLATEFORMS USED</h2>\n<ul class="services-logos"><li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/bs-logo.png" alt="Bootstrap"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/html5-logo.png" alt="HTML5"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/css3-logo.png" alt="CSS3"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/jquery-logo.png" alt="jQuery"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/ss-logo.png" alt="SilverStripe"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/wp-logo.png" alt="WordPress"></li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n</section>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 3, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0, NULL),
