(158, 6, 24, 1, 1, 1, 'ServicePage', '2016-08-01 10:24:37', '2016-04-14 05:57:06', 'service', 'My Services', 'Service', '<section class="services-items-section normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h1>WHAT I CAN DO FOR YOU</h1>\n</div>\n<div class="row row-flex row-flex-wrap">\n<div class="col-md-4">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-desktop fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>The websites I design and develop for you is owned by you 100%. All images, text and photos are yours. There are no ties once finished.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-4">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-wrench fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>I offer ongoing services and updates of all sites when needed. I am there when you need me.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col-md-4">\n<div class="services-item"><span><i class="fa fa-code fa-4x fa-icons"></i></span>\n<p>I design, code and test your website to make sure working for all devices before I release the website to you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="services-section"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-edit fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>WEB DESIGN</h3>\n<p>I design websites for small business, organizations, and personal websites. Your website is designed to fulfill your expectations, and your customers expectations. It\'s important that your website looks good to engage your visitors, allowing your website to become successful and meet the goals you are striving for.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-code fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>WEB DEVELOPMENT</h3>\n<p>I custom develop all websites, allowing them to remain unique, scalable and to function as required. Your website will perform better, be more efficient, and overall it will provide a better experience for you and your users. Whatever your idea, I can turn it in to a reality.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-html5 fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>HTML5 &amp; CSS3</h3>\n<p>I create websites that use the latest HTML5 and CSS3 and Bootstrap technology, this allows me to deliver cutting edge functionality in a beautiful responsive website designs. With more businesses online than ever before, distinguishing yourself from the crowd has never been more essential for your business to succeed.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br><br><div class="row">\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-search fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>SEO</h3>\n<p>Everyone understands the importance of getting their website listed on the first page of Google. I carry out SEO practices on every page of every website I create, allowing your site to rank higher in search engine results - potentially driving more traffic to your site.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-mobile fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>MOBILE RESPONSIVE</h3>\n<p>Are you missing out on mobile devices? If you don’t have a mobile website, then you are missing out on customers. I use the latest “responsive design” techniques to ensure your business website works well on any mobile devices, as it does on a desktop or laptop.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-tasks fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>CONTENT MANAGEMENT</h3>\n<p>All websites are built using a Content Management System in either WordPress or SilverStripe. This allowing you to keep your websites content updated and current, with no knowledge of HTML or web development skills. You are able to manage your website yourself, from anywhere at anytime.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br><br><div class="row">\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-camera fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>PHOTOGRAPHY</h3>\n<p>A lot of clients require photos taken of their work or business to put on their website. I can help with this. I will arrange a date and time with you and then arrive and take pictures for you.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-server fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>WEBSITE HOSTING</h3>\n<p>I offer hosting and domain name for your website without you worrying about what you need to buy or what add on you may or may not need. All I do need to know is the desired domain name you wish to use for your website. If you already have a domain name and hosting for your website, don’t worry.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-4"><i class="fa fa-wrench fa-5x"></i>\n<h3>WEBSITE RE-DESIGN</h3>\n<p>Is your website a few years old, looking tired and need of a makeover? Did you maybe try putting it together yourself by using free website templates or software but realized it doesn’t look professional? Customers will always look at your website before contacting you, so your company’s first impression is crucial to get right.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section><section class="single-container normal-bg"><div class="container">\n<div class="row">\n<h2>TOOLS AND PLATEFORMS USED</h2>\n<ul class="services-logos"><li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/bs-logo.png" alt="Bootstrap"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/html5-logo.png" alt="HTML5"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/css3-logo.png" alt="CSS3"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/jquery-logo.png" alt="jQuery"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/ss-logo.png" alt="SilverStripe"></li>\n<li><img title="" src="themes/snapwebdesigns/images/logos/wp-logo.png" alt="WordPress"></li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n</section>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 3, 0, 0, NULL, 'Inherit', 'Inherit', 0, NULL),
